text: Gilbert J. Henderson (5 September 1926 - 30 January 2017) was a Canadian sports shooter. He competed in the trap event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1926 births Category:2017 deaths Category:Canadian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Canada Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Toronto
